name: IN THE GARDEN OF MY MIND

metadata.name: IN THE GARDEN OF MY MIND - 001
metadata.description:
"If you need me, I'll be sitting in my garden watching as the universe pours forth around me. Everything breathes in unison. Every fiber of my body feels at home. I hope you also find peace in my garden." - Scribble Warlock

Digital Drawing // 5000 x 5000 @ 600 DPI
